<table width="70%">
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <th>Consensus Policy Making</th>
    </tr>

    <tr>
      <td>
        <p>APNIC policies are decided by the Asia Pacific community in a consensus decision-making process that is:</p>

        <p style="font-size:1.5em;margin-top:-0.5em;">Open - Transparent - Bottom-up</p>
      </td>
    </tr>

    <tr>
      <th>Participate in the Policy Process</th>
    </tr>

    <tr>
      <td><a href="http://www.apnic.net/community/participate/join-discussions/sigs/policy-sig">Policy SIG Page</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href="http://www.apnic.net/community/policy/process">Development process</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href="http://mailman.apnic.net/mailing-lists/sig-policy/">Mailing List Archive</a></td>
    </tr>

    <tr>
      <td><a href="http://mailman.apnic.net/mailman/listinfo/sig-policy">Subscribe to Mailing list</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href="http://www.apnic.net/policy/proposals">Policy proposal archive</a>&nbsp; |&nbsp; <a href="http://www.apnic.net/community/policy/process/template" class="ppt">Presentation template</a>&nbsp;</td>
